summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2015 JEEP CHEROKEE. WHEN THE CONTACT PARKED THE VEHICLE, IT FAILED TO RESTART. WHEN THE CONTACT MADE ANOTHER ATTEMPT, THE VEHICLE RESTARTED. THE FAILURE OCCURRED SEVERAL TIMES. THE CONTACT ALSO STATED THAT WHEN THE VEHICLE WAS IN ANY GEAR, IT JERKED AND MADE A LOUD NOISE. ALSO, THE TRANSMISSION INDICATOR BLINKED ON AND OFF. ON ANOTHER OCCASION, WHEN THE VEHICLE WAS STARTED, THE RPMS INCREASED VERY HIGH WITHOUT THE ACCELERATOR PEDAL BEING PRESSED. JIM BROWNE CHRYSLER JEEP DODGE RAM OF DADE CITY (12020 US-301, DADE CITY, FL 33525, (352) 353-0704) ADVISED THAT THE VEHICLE BE BROUGHT IN FOR DIAGNOSTIC TESTING. THE MANUFACTURER AGREED WITH THE DEALER. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 50,000.
